transcript:
[Ringing]
Executive: Hello. 
Executive: Ji sir very good afternoon. Kaise hain? Sorry very good evening.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Ji sir kaise hain?
Executive: Actually main senior manager baat kar rahi thi sir India Mart team se. Aapka Bharat se discussion ho gaya sir?
Customer: Madam main jis jagah mein hoon us jagah se baat karna mushkil hai aap bhi sun sakte hain piche baat. 
Executive: Kitni kitne time call back karu aapko?
Customer: Aaj aaj nahi hoga kal sham ko.
Executive: Achcha kal kar lu. Chaliye theek hai sir.
summary:
Concerns:

- Difficulty in having a conversation due to background noise.



Resolution:

- Call to be rescheduled.



Next Steps: 

- Call to be rescheduled for tomorrow evening.



Alert (If Any):

None

reschedule, callback
